RasterFunctionTemplate.Name: GSSICB_Amplitude_dB_MinMax
RasterFunctionTemplate.Description: Calculates gamma-0 dB from the backscatter DN values of the Global Seasonal Sentinel-1 Interferometric Coherence and Backscatter datatset. A Min-Max stretch is applied.

Function.Name: Stretch
Function.Description: Enhances an image by adjusting the range of values displayed. This does not alter the underlying pixel values. If a pixel has a value outside of the specified range, it will appear as either the minimum or maximum value.

Function.Name: Calculator
Function.Description: Computes a raster from a raster based mathematical expression.
